Maps support
- Index on mapKeys(val)
-- Map itself should not be passed as argument
-- SELECT on mapKeys(val)
foo	1
FOO	1
BAR	2
Baz	3
foo	1
FOO	1
BAR	2
Baz	3
-- SELECT on mapValues(val) (fallback)
foo	1
BAR	2
Baz	3
foo	1
BAR	2
Baz	3
- Index on mapValues(val)
